title: Gorgeous young female doctor-mom bludgeoned DEAD, still in heels. The suspect revealed! PART 2

description:
Doctor Teresa Sievers beaten with a hammer in her own home. Surprising suspects are revealed. Joining Nancy Grace to uncover the suspects is: Jason Oshins NY, defense attorney; Jeff Cortese, Former FBI special Agent; Sheryl McCollum, Forensics Expert & Cold Case Investigative Research Institute Founder; Dr Tim Gallagher, Medical Examiner for State of Florida; Dr Bethany Marshall, Psychoanalyst; Amanda Hall, reporter WINK TV Ft Myers Florida.
